To run the test cases follow below steps :
Import the project as maven project 
Navigate to test/java/TestRunner you will find TestRunner.java class 
Right click the class and run
It will execute all the test casess for categories API
The test framework if Cucumber BDD based and for sending API requests I have used Java Rest Assured library , BDD test cases are defined in /java/test/resources
The framework contains utilities section which contains all the reusable libraries
